title: Aleco BioMarkt
description: Part of chain health shop. Stocks a variety of vegan food products including mock meats from producers like Wheaty, Taifun and Viana. There are also many types of vegan milk alternatives like soy, rice and oat drinks and some other things like vegan chocolate spread. A bistro is integrated into the building that offers small snacks like soup, salad, and pattys.
